column4: This is the fight of our lives. We are going to win, whatever it takes. - Captain America
History is your future. One day, you will meet yourself back where you started, but stronger. - Beyoncé
I have to sing, I have to play. The music, it’s not just in me, it is me. - Coco
How happy is the blameless vestal's lot! The world forgetting, by the world forgot. - Mary
Life moves pretty fast. If you don't stop and look around once in a while, you could miss it. — Ferris Bueller
